OL,5,G1700 Indian Ocean with Simon Reeve
OL,6,     FSouth Africa to Zanzibar: Simon
OL,7,     Ftravels around the coastline of
OL,8,     Fthe Indian Ocean, setting out from
OL,9,     FSouth Africa - where he dives with
OL,10,     Fsharks - and moving on to
OL,11,     FMozambique and Zanzibar.
OL,12,G1800 Indian Ocean with Simon Reeve
OL,13,     FMadagascar to the Seychelles:
OL,14,     FSimon's journey takes him
OL,15,     Fspearfishing in Madagascar,
OL,16,     Fthrough the slums of Mauritius and
OL,17,     Fon to the Seychelles, where he
OL,18,     Fvisits the world's smallest
OL,19,     Fnational park.
